Subject: Re: [T2] Hose for external oil cooler - keeps spliting

[...]
highly recommend the fittings john has mentioned.  Bus engines cold can 
and do hit 80 psi.  cheap rubber will not take that very long and hose 
clamps will leak at that pressure.  the -8 fittings are pricey but i  
consider them worth the cost.
jimt
